/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多野睇"},{"pid":"686c7236000fee70d4d06998db2091243ee7570f","tid":25413,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"如果唔計tips,份糧有幾低？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51d0fd360998224415ae4c0d0f4cefd2f77b1ff","tid":25413,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收入幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係做pt,番夜5:30-9:30<br />\n<br />\n淨收入一晚80左右<br />\n<br />\n計埋油錢一日大慨70<br />\n即4個鐘500幾港紙"},{"pid":"0d84461ad835ddc80823c67b673566b8d34584b6","tid":25413,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"點夠生活"},{"pid":"14ec33dea5d1be93edf31724157debe06ff2a8a3","tid":25413,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔計tips,份糧有幾低？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地果度就一單外賣一定收最少1蚊外賣費，會因距離而增，最遠試過5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要上高速10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n時薪就6蚊，我一個鐘大慨3張單，所以得9蚊左右，<br />\n<br />\n72港紙一個鐘（唔計tips)"},{"pid":"262aa160480b58fa9555dba1ac83918bcbda1a8d","tid":25413,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點夠生活</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係留學生黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身老母有生活費但係呢份工夠我比屋租同埋所有日常開支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef64d8cae99b2d688406879101ffadc0a3c8a55","tid":25413,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩甜故</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同過送過幾次既客......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma